The art of arrival, redesigned. ✨
 
SW+ partnered with the Charleston Place Hotel to redesign the main entry plaza and create a more welcoming arrival experience. The project relocated the drop-off and short-term parking from Market Street to Meeting Street and added shaded seating areas for hotel guests and pedestrians enjoying the surrounding shopping district. The result is a refreshed space that blends comfort, functionality, and Charleston charm.

